::TypedStructLiterals
  I think this was meant to parse this:
  p2 := Vec3(float) { 4, 5, 6 };
  This should probably be written as this anyways:
  p2 := cast(Vec3(float), {4, 5, 6 });
  or whatever the cast syntax will be

